      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">16.302</ph> Cost contracts.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d988e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1016e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Description.</i> A cost contract is a cost-reimbursement contract in which the contractor receives no fee.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1016e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Application</i>. A cost contract may be appropriate for research and development work, particularly with nonprofit educational institutions or other nonprofit organizations.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1016e24">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
